So the weapon used to kill Mr. Faraday is actually the key the Yatagarasu stole... <textEffects>(This piece of information is more critical than anything we've learned up until now!)</textEffects>
</line><line><textEffects>Yatagarasu's Key data updated in my Organizer.</textEffects>
</line><line>Franziska:
...Frankly, I'm shocked.
</line><line>Edgeworth:
