<line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(It's simply not possible for the killer to have escaped through barred windows... ...and yet, the fragrance of the perfume managed to escape from Defendant Lobby No. 1. Of course! Incorporeal things ccan move freely through these <span style="color:green"><span class="hidden"><span class="explain" style="text-decoration: underline dotted" title="Open windows - The criminal couldn&#39;t have made it through, but what about incorporeal things?">open, barred windows</textEffects></span><textEffects> (Open windows - The criminal couldn't have made it through, but what about incorporeal things?)</textEffects></span>!)</span>
