</line><line>Franziska:
That's true. This courthouse does seem to be well-designed for such a thing, as it were.
</line><line>Edgeworth:
However, what happened in reality was... ...Detective Gumshoe, Detective Badd, and Ms. Yew... All three of them heard the gunshot.
</line><line>Franziska:
