</line><line>Franziska:
But why was that necessary in the first place? I want a real answer, Miles! I demand satisfaction!
</line><line>Edgeworth:
Very well. I believe that the killer wanted to manipulate our perception of a certain fact. <textEffects>(What was it that the killer wanted to manipulate our perception of?)</textEffects>
</line>



<line>Edgeworth:
