<line>Franziska:
It sounds like the exact same story he told us before...
</line><line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(This is were it really starts. I mustn't let my guard down for even a second, or the truth will blow away. Now is the time to put the patented Von Karma "perfect proof" to the test!)</textEffects>
