<line>Franziska:
Miles, her testimony... is flawless.
</line><line>Edgeworth:
...Yes, but no matter what sort of trick she may try to pull, she won't escape me! <textEffects>(And if I'm lacking in information, I'll just draw it out of her!)</textEffects>
