<textEffects>Accusing someone of murder over a spilled bottle of perfume is a bit over the top.</textEffects>
</line>

<line>Yew:
<textEffects>But I suppose forgery of evidence is to be expected of a disciple of Von Karma.</textEffects>
</line>

<line>Yew:
<textEffects>In any case, it simply could not have been me who killed Mr. Faraday.</textEffects>
